title: Future Ops Online Premium v1.1.38 APK
description:
<a href="http://i.imgur.com/BXBvi.jpg" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://i.imgur.com/BXBvi.jpg</a>


Future Ops Online Premium play.google.com.FutureOpsOnlinePremium
Premium Supporters now have a few days of sneak peek access to brand new Work In Progress features as a thank you for your help.

COOP Survival MMO Mode is now available to everyone, however its under heavy reconstruction right now, many features had to be disabled in order to optimize them for mobile devices, including picking up weapons, buildings must be simplified.

Premium Supporters will soon receive early access to PVP MMO Mode which is identical to COOP, except you can kill other players to have them drop their gun, and give you xp and virtual currency. This will be built during January.

A Multiplayer First Person Shooter with up to 44 Players in COOP Survival MMO, Team Deathmatch and Capture The Point game modes.

Air Vehicles allow you to play Mobile FPS games like never before, this game aims to be your mobile battlefield, for Free!

Please always update your game, if there are server side changes, then a new server version is created that is only accessible by the newest version of the game, which is why it looks like there are no servers online.

What's in this version : (Updated : Sep 2, 2013)
Re-Added Prebaked Shadows to The Docks
Added Option for Advanced Water
Added Option for Red Injured Screen Fill
Glare Effect Lowered- Greatly Increased Rendering Performance
Bug Fixes in Zombie Island.
Added Lens Glare Effect
Fixed night maps Low Quality Shader
Increased Rendering Performance- Removed Prebaked Shadows on The Docks
Added Early Test version of the new map Zombie Island (16x larger than Zombie Jungle)
Removed Prebaked Shadows from Zombie Infested Jungle for performance
Added Optional Real Time Shadows
Disabled Map Builder temporarily
Required Android O/S : 2.2+
